# clean brackets
import re
def clean_text(text):
    # Remove brackets 
    cleaned_text = re.sub(r'[\(\)]', '', text)
    return cleaned_text
df['cleaned'] = df['title'].apply(lambda x: clean_text(x) if pd.notnull(x) else [])
